The moment you realize you're getting older - from child to teen, from teen to young adult, young adult to mid-life, from mid-life to maturity, from maturity to death, you grieve. Whenever there's transition there is grief. And it is the strength of the grief that will usher you in to the next level of your own conscious evolution.
